WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Dad asked me to take a gift to Toko-san, so I took the gift to her after school.

00:07.710 --> 00:12.400
Toko-san seemed tired and slow.

00:13.040 --> 00:15.320
She didn’t even open the gift’s wrapping paper.

00:16.190 --> 00:17.720
I wonder why she was tired.

00:18.200 --> 00:19.720
I wonder what the gift was.

00:20.080 --> 00:21.360
Could it have been cosmetics?

00:21.840 --> 00:25.200
Mom has a lot of cosmetics, too.

00:25.880 --> 00:28.670
I guess I’ll use cosmetics one day, too.

00:29.200 --> 00:31.720
I won’t look very good if I used cosmetics now.

00:32.400 --> 00:36.360
Misato-chan looks grown up anyway, so cosmetics should look good on her.

00:37.050 --> 00:42.300
Oh, Dad said there were some extra presents, so I’ll take some for Misato-chan.
